Package: grimoire
Title: Fetch and Manage 'RLadies+' Agent Skills from 'GitHub'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Athanasia Monika", "Mowinckel", , "a.m.mowinckel@psykologi.uio.no", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A 'usethis'-style client for the 'RLadies+' grimoire of Agent
    Skills. Fetches individual skills from the 'rladies/grimoire' 'GitHub'
    repository into a local project, keeps them in sync with upstream
    releases, and removes them again without clobbering hand edits.
    Skills fetched this way work with any tool that reads the Agent Skills
    format, not only 'Claude'.
